WEBVTT

00:04:27.670 --> 00:04:31.916
(Gelak tawa)

00:04:31.916 --> 00:04:33.850
Senyap di hujung talian.

00:04:35.160 --> 00:04:38.160
Kemudian, dia berkata,

00:04:38.160 --> 00:04:40.120
"Saya perlu tanya isteri saya."

00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:41.520
(Gelak tawa)

00:04:41.520 --> 00:04:42.756
Apa?

00:04:42.756 --> 00:04:44.196
Rasis ini ada isteri?

00:04:44.196 --> 00:04:45.906
(Gelak tawa)

00:04:46.076 --> 00:04:48.766
Beberapa hari kemudian,
kami bertemu di rumahnya.

00:04:49.156 --> 00:04:53.444
Saya tak akan lupa
apabila dia membuka pintu

00:04:53.444 --> 00:04:56.134
dan menghulurkan tangan
untuk bersalaman dengan saya.

00:04:56.884 --> 00:04:58.924
Saya rasa amat kecewa.

00:04:58.924 --> 00:05:00.164
(Gelak tawa)